<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Ali Hassan — AI Developer</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;700;800&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --gold: #f5c842;
    --gold2: #e0a800;
    --cyan: #00ffe7;
    --dark: #050a0e;
    --dark2: #0b1520;
    --dark3: #0f1e2e;
    --white: #f0f4f8;
    --muted: #7a90a0;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: none;
  }

  /* CUSTOM CURSOR */
  .cursor {
    position: fixed;
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    transition: transform 0.1s, width 0.2s, height 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
  }
  .cursor-ring {
    position: fixed;
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9998;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    transition: transform 0.18s ease, width 0.2s, height 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  /* CANVAS BG */
  #bg-canvas {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.2rem 4rem;
    background: rgba(5,10,14,0.7);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.08);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .nav-links a::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -4px; left: 0;
    width: 0; height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    transition: width 0.3s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
  .nav-links a:hover::after { width: 100%; }

  /* SECTIONS */
  section {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 7rem 4rem 4rem;
  }

  /* HERO */
  #hero {
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-tag {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 8rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold) 0%, #fff8d0 50%, var(--gold2) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.5s forwards;
  }

  .hero-role {
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1.15rem);
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.7s forwards;
  }

  .hero-role span { color: var(--gold); }

  .hero-cta {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.9s forwards;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.85rem 2.2rem;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    cursor: none;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--dark);
    font-weight: 700;
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(245,200,66,0.3);
  }
  .btn-secondary {
    border: 2px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.3);
    color: var(--gold);
    background: transparent;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(245,200,66,0.05);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(245,200,66,0.15);
  }

  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2.5rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease 1.5s forwards;
  }
  .scroll-hint span {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 50px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), transparent);
    animation: scrollDrop 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* ABOUT */
  #about {
    flex-direction: row;
    gap: 6rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-3d {
    flex: 0 0 280px;
    height: 320px;
    perspective: 800px;
  }

  .card-3d {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    animation: float3d 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .card-face {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark2), var(--dark3));
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.15);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(245,200,66,0.1);
  }

  .avatar-ring {
    width: 110px; height: 110px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(245,200,66,0.3);
  }
  .avatar-ring::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(245,200,66,0.3);
    animation: spin 10s linear infinite;
  }
  .avatar-initials {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .card-name {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .card-title {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--cyan);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .card-badges {
    display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;
  }
  .badge {
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    background: rgba(245,200,66,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.2);
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .about-text { flex: 1; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .section-label::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-para {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.9;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .about-para span { color: var(--gold); }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .stat-box {
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(245,200,66,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.1);
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .stat-box:hover {
    background: rgba(245,200,66,0.08);
    border-color: rgba(245,200,66,0.3);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }

  /* SKILLS */
  #skills {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .skills-header { text-align: center; }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .skill-card {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.08);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.8rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    cursor: none;
  }
  .skill-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--cyan));
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .skill-card:hover { border-color: rgba(245,200,66,0.2); transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .skill-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }

  .skill-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .skill-name {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .skill-bar-bg {
    height: 3px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .skill-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--cyan));
    border-radius: 2px;
    width: 0;
    transition: width 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
  }
  .skill-pct {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .skill-tags {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .skill-tag {
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    background: rgba(0,255,231,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,231,0.15);
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--cyan);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  /* PROJECTS */
  #projects {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .projects-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .project-card {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.08);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    cursor: none;
    position: relative;
  }
  .project-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(245,200,66,0.25);
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .project-thumb {
    height: 160px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .project-thumb::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0.15;
  }
  .p1 .project-thumb { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d2137, #1a3a5c); }
  .p2 .project-thumb { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0d37, #3a1a5c); }
  .p3 .project-thumb { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d3718, #1a5c2f); }
  .p4 .project-thumb { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #371a0d, #5c3a1a); }
  .p5 .project-thumb { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d3037, #1a505c); }

  .project-body { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .project-tag {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .project-name {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .project-desc {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .project-stack {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .stack-tag {
    padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
    background: rgba(245,200,66,0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.15);
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* EDUCATION */
  #education {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), transparent);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    padding-left: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    position: relative;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateX(-20px);
    transition: all 0.6s ease;
  }
  .timeline-item.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateX(0);
  }
  .timeline-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -5px;
    top: 4px;
    width: 11px; height: 11px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--gold);
  }
  .timeline-year {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .timeline-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .timeline-sub {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .timeline-desc {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* CONTACT */
  #contact {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .contact-card {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.08);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    cursor: none;
  }
  .contact-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(245,200,66,0.05);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }
  .contact-icon { font-size: 1.6rem; }
  .contact-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .contact-value {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    word-break: break-all;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-tagline {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .contact-sub {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,200,66,0.06);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }
  footer span { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes float3d {
    0%, 100% { transform: rotateX(5deg) rotateY(-8deg) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: rotateX(-5deg) rotateY(8deg) translateY(-12px); }
  }
  @keyframes scrollDrop {
    0% { transform: scaleY(0); transform-origin: top; opacity: 1; }
    50% { transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: top; opacity: 1; }
    100% { transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: bottom; opacity: 0; }
  }
  @keyframes spin {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links { gap: 1.2rem; }
    section { padding: 6rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
    #about { flex-direction: column; gap: 3rem; }
    .about-3d { flex: none; width: 220px; height: 260px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .about-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Custom Cursor -->
<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>

<!-- Animated BG Canvas -->
<canvas id="bg-canvas"></canvas>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="#hero" class="nav-logo">AH</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
    <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
    <li><a href="#education">Education</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-tag">⚡ Available for Opportunities — Pakistan</div>
  <h1 class="hero-name">Ali Hassan</h1>
  <p class="hero-role">AI Developer &amp; <span>ML Engineer</span> in the Making</p>
  <div class="hero-cta">
    <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">View Projects</a>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Get in Touch</a>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint">
    <span>Scroll</span>
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="about-3d">
    <div class="card-3d">
      <div class="card-face">
        <div class="avatar-ring">
          <span class="avatar-initials">AH</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-name">Ali Hassan</div>
        <div class="card-title">AI / ML Developer</div>
        <div class="card-badges">
          <span class="badge">Pakistan 🇵🇰</span>
          <span class="badge">Multan</span>
          <span class="badge">Open to Work</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-text">
    <div class="section-label">About Me</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Building the<br><span style="color:var(--gold)">Future</span> with AI</h2>
    <p class="about-para">
      I'm a <span>BS Artificial Intelligence</span> student at the University of Southern Punjab, Multan — passionate about turning complex problems into intelligent solutions.
    </p>
    <p class="about-para">
      My focus lies in <span>Deep Learning</span>, <span>Machine Learning</span>, and building real-world AI products. I've conceptualized multiple AI ventures including a Jarvis-style assistant (<span>Alix</span>), smart translation headphones, and AI-powered restaurant management systems.
    </p>
    <p class="about-para">
      Actively seeking <span>fully funded undergraduate opportunities in China</span> to accelerate my AI journey and contribute to the future of technology.
    </p>
    <div class="about-stats">
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div class="stat-num">5+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">AI Projects</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div class="stat-num">3+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Platforms</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div class="stat-num">∞</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Ambition</div>
      </div>
    </div>
